title: 镁凯利克金属成型加工油
data: 铝片,硅钢片,镀锌薄板 stainless stee non-ferrous metals, Silicon Steel
特为薄片金属的闱剪及碾轧而研制,加工后能快速挥发干净,在大多的后加工工序中也不用清洗。 Only leaving an extremel light protecting film on the metals parts, which need not to be cleaned at most of the subsequent handing
低/中碳钢,铝,有色金属 low/medium carbon steel, aluminum, non-ferrous metals

挥发速度快,无气味,不含任何有害物质,不含硫、氯、硅。Hjgh evaporating speed, without odor, without any injuant, free of sulfur, chlorine and silicone主要用于空调器中铝散热片的冲裁、钢管的弯管和涨管工艺。也用于相应的计算机和电子元件的冲压,特别适用于象硅钢类易腐蚀材料。 Mainly forstamping air- conditionradiator,blending steel tube. Also for stamping computer and electric part,especially for silicone steel
中碳合金不锈钢,铝,有色金属,硅钢片等 medium carbon/ alloyed/ stainless steel,non-ferrous mesas, Silicon Steel.

低粘度快干式冲压、拉伸用油。具有较高的极压性能和较快的挥发速度。 Low viscosity, fast-evaporating stamping and punching oil. it has a high EP perform ance and quick volatilization speed主要用于硅钢片等微型电机定子、转子的冲裁,也可用于镀锌薄板的冲裁加工。Mainly for silicon steel as stamping of minisize electric engine stator and rotor, also for stamping of thin galvanized sheet ngine
中碳高合金/不锈钢,有色金属mediumcarbon/high alloy/stainless,steelnon-ferrous mesas

高极压性能,对铜不产生腐蚀。Hight EP performance, no corrosion to copper.用于钢板的冲压成型V41用于厚度小于10mm板材,V40用于厚度小于2mm板材。 Mainly for steel pressing or forming operations V41 suitable for platethichness less than 10mm, V40 is suitabl for plate thickness less than 2mm
